OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FThe Government has to "do better" to
OL,7,Fensure learning environments are "fit
OL,8,Ffor learning", the leader of a
OL,9,Fheadteachers' union will say.
OL,11,FGeoff Barton, general secretary of the
OL,12,FAssociation of School and College
OL,13,FLeaders (ASCL), will say the condition
OL,14,Fof many school and college buildings
OL,15,Fis "simply shocking".
OL,17,FIn a speech at the union's annual
OL,18,Fconference on Saturday in Liverpool,
OL,19,FMr Barton will say many schools have
OL,20,Fto "scrabble for cash" to afford the
OL,21,Fcosts of basic repairs and maintenance.
