OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FHis comments come as a survey for the
OL,7,FASCL found that more than half (57%)
OL,8,Fof teachers and school leaders said
OL,9,Ftheir classrooms are too hot in the
OL,10,Fsummer because of poor ventilation.
OL,12,FThe poll by the Teacher Tapp app asked
OL,13,F8,585 teachers and leaders in state
OL,14,Fschools in England in February about
OL,15,Fthe condition of the classroom they
OL,16,Fhad most recently taught in.
