OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FMore than a quarter (28%) said they
OL,7,Fwere too cold because of inadequate
OL,8,Fheating systems and nearly a fifth
OL,9,F(19%) said windows and doors were
OL,10,Fbroken and 19% reported poor electrics.
OL,12,FAround one in seven (15%) said they
OL,13,Fhad recently taught in classrooms with
OL,14,Fleaking ceilings.
OL,16,FIn his final address to the union's
OL,17,Fannual conference before stepping down
OL,18,Fin April, Mr Barton will say the
OL,19,Ffindings show the "pressure on the
OL,20,Fground".
