OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FHe will say: "Not only has capital
OL,7,Finvestment been wholly inadequate but
OL,8,Ftortuous funding systems mean many
OL,9,Fschools have to scrabble for cash
OL,10,Fthrough a bidding process ` just to
OL,11,Fafford the cost of basic repairs and
OL,12,Fmaintenance.
OL,14,F"It is surely obvious that Government
OL,15,Fhas to do better than this ` that
OL,16,Flearning environments have to be fit
OL,17,Ffor learning."
