OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FA report by the National Audit Office
OL,7,F(NAO) published in June last year
OL,8,Fconcluded that around 700,000 pupils
OL,9,Fare learning in a school that the
OL,10,Fresponsible body or Department for
OL,11,FEducation believes "needs major
OL,12,Frebuilding or refurbishment" following
OL,13,Fyears of "underinvestment".
OL,15,FMr Barton will also call on all
OL,16,Fpolitical parties to improve revenue
OL,17,Ffunding for education over the course
OL,18,Fof the next parliament.
