OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FHe will say: "Population estimates
OL,7,Fpredict that the number of pupils in
OL,8,FEngland's schools will fall by half a
OL,9,Fmillion over the next five years. It
OL,10,Fadds up to a huge multibillion-pound
OL,11,Fsaving.
OL,13,F"So, instead of raking this money back
OL,14,Finto the Treasury ` there is a golden
OL,15,Fopportunity to put education on a more
OL,16,Fsustainable footing.
OL,26,@nD@NOUuD@AOU
