OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,F"Use this money to raise the rate of
OL,7,Fper-pupil funding, and the pupil
OL,8,Fpremium. It's a policy that costs
OL,9,Fnothing ` or at least nothing extra `
OL,10,Fbut it would make a world of
OL,11,Fdifference to children and young
OL,12,Fpeople, and particularly those from
OL,13,Fdisadvantaged homes."
OL,15,FMr Barton is stepping down in April
OL,16,Fafter seven years as the general
OL,17,Fsecretary of the ASCL.
OL,19,FHe will be succeeded by Pepe Di'Iasio,
OL,20,Fcurrently headteacher of Wales High
OL,21,FSchool in Rotherham.
