OL,3,CGovernment 'must do better to ensure
OL,4,Cclassrooms are fit for learning'
OL,6,FIn his final speech as the union's
OL,7,Fleader, Mr Barton will tell hundreds
OL,8,Fof school and college leaders that
OL,9,Fthere is a need to "look again at the
OL,10,Fsubstance of education" with a "laser-
OL,11,Flike review" of the national
OL,12,Fcurriculum.
OL,14,FHe will also call for an end to the
OL,15,F"snobby obsession" with academic
OL,16,Fversus technical education.
